title: #92Noon! Twins Done/Florio/Burns/Charch/Gleeman
description: Twins season comes to an end, Florio's weekly hit make up the first hour. More positive notes with Ryan Burns in studio on the 5-0 Gophers, Charch's pickup join midway through, then Aaron Gleeman in studio for entire final hour for a wrap on the baseball team.
